// 1. How is the routing achieved in next.js app?

//      => File-system based routing mechanism
//      => When a file is added to the pages folder in a project,
//         by default all the files becomes available as a route.


//  2. How is Dynamic routing done in next.js?

//      => Create a .js file with square brackets [xyz]
//      => import useRouter hook and create a router object
//      => create pageNumber = router.query.xyz